{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee palibdseja Dahwi-\ndam prett (to Amalekitetu)\nSixrotajeem/ jo tee bija wiſſi\nſipri warrent Wiḥri/ un bija\nKaxxa Ahwerſti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir ikdeenas nahze pee\nDahwida winnam par Paligu/\nteekams tas Lehgeris tik leels tap-\npe/ ka weens Deewa Lehgeris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ſchee irr to Wirfineeku\nPulki/ kas us Kaxxu apbrunnno-\njahs/ un pee Dahwidu uhs Ee-\nbronn nahze/ ka tee Saula Keh-\nnixa Walstu winnam peegreestu/\npehz ta KUNGA Wahrdu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "To Behrnu Juhda/ kas\npreekſchturramas Bruknas un\nSchkehpus neffe/ bija feſch tuhſ-\nſochi un aſtonſimts us Kaxxu\ngattawi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Sihmeana Behrneeni\nbija / ſeptin tuhſtoſchi nn ſimts\nſipri warrent Kaxxa-Wiḥri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Lewja Behrneem /\ntſchetri tuhſtoſchi un feſchſimts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jojadus bija to Aa-\nroniteru Waldneeks/ un ar to\ntrihs tuhſtoſchi un ſeptinsimts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Zadaks weens ſiprs\nwarrens Puifs/ un no winna\nTehwa Namma bija diwideſmits\ndiwi Leeli-Kungi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no Benjaminna Behr-\nneem bija Saula Brahtu trihs\ntuhſtoſchi/ jo ſthds tam Laſkam\nbtja Daudi/ kas wehl pee Saula\nNamuna turrejahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no Eewraima Behr-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no Manaffus pu\nZilts aſtonpadefimits tuhſtoſch\nkas pee Wahrdeem faukti etu\nka tee nahktu Dahwidu par K\nninu eezelt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no Ibsaschara Bet-\nneem/ kas Laikus gudri ſapr-\nte/ kas Israekain bij jada-\nto paſchu Wirfineeku bija di-\nſimts/ un wiſſi winnu Bra-\ndarrija pehz winnu Wahrda.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Sebulana/ kas Ka-\nxâ iſgahje ar wiſſadahm Ka-\nBruknahm apbrunnotti/ b-\npeeſdefimits tuhſtoſchi/ ar dr-\nfchu Sirdi ſawa Kahrtâ ee-\nRaufchanas ſtahwedami.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no Nauṭalus b-\ntuhſtoſchi Leeli-Kungi/ un-\nteem trihsdeſmits ſeptin tuhſ-\nſchi/ kas preekſchturramas Bru-\nnas un Schkehpus walkaja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no teem Daniteeer-\nkas us Kaxxu gattawi bija/\nwideſmits un aſton tuhſtoſ-\nun feſchſimts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no Ahsera/ kas Ka-\nrâ iſgahje us Raufchanu ga-\nwi/bija tſchetrideſmits tuhſtoſ-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no teem pahr Jar-\nneefcheem/ no teem Ruhbent-\nreem/ un Gaditeeem un pi-\nZilti Manaffus/ ar wiſſada-\nKaxxu-Bruknahm/ ſimts un-\nwideſmits tuhſtoſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſi ſchee Kaxxa-Wiḥ-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
